><li>Whose side will you take in this story without heroes? Branching paths and multiple endings allow for a custom experience or opportunity for replay. Choose Loretta’s fate and explore the multiple opportunities as they present themselves to her.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592540/extras/527fea62851da16eb8e677e86d05137e.poster.avif?t=1772597987\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592540/extras/527fea62851da16eb8e677e86d05137e.webm?t=1772597987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592540/extras/527fea62851da16eb8e677e86d05137e.mp4?t=1772597987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
